      "text": "<p>Treba dodati element <code>div</code>-a sa klasom <code>well</code> unutar svakog vašeg elementa <code>div</code> sa klasom <code>col-xs-6</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "const wells = document.querySelectorAll('div.col-xs-6 > div.well');\r\nassert.lengthOf( wells,2 ); "
